A possible IoT project.

A high performance MCU/MPU with following features-

Analog- ADC, DAC
Control- 16/24 bit timers, PWM motor control
Memory Controller- SDRAM, SDMMC, QSPI flash
Communication- UART, SPI, QSPI, I2C, SMBUS, USB HS/FS/OTG, CAN, Ethernet
Wireless- ? - BLE, Thread, Matter, LoRA, Zigbee
Display- u/HDMI, LCD
Audio- ?
